/*!
\page reset.html
\title SAM-BA reset applet
\brief This document explains how to execute the \b {reset} applet

\section1 Resetting the target

The \b {reset} applet writes into the Control Register (CR) of the Reset
Controller (RSTC) to reset the SAM MPU device on the target. Depending on the
board design, other peripherals such as external NVM may or may not be reset as
well.

\code
sam-ba -p <port> -d <device> -a reset

$ sam-ba -p serial -d sama5d2 -a reset
\endcode
*/
